{
  "id": "66d2143b7f576c001cd60677",
  "title": "ADHD向けタスク管理システムの設計案",
  "created": 1725043784,
  "updated": 1725043839,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "66d2143b7f576c001cd60677",
      "text": "ADHD向けタスク管理システムの設計案",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1725043784,
      "updated": 1725043784
    },
    {
      "id": "66d21474aff09e000048c399",
      "text": "[claude.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1725043829,
      "updated": 1725043832
    },
    {
      "id": "66d21447aff09e000048c35f",
      "text": "主要機能",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1725043784,
      "updated": 1725043784
    },
    {
      "id": "66d21447aff09e000048c361",
      "text": "\t\"[やらないこと]\"リスト",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1725043784,
      "updated": 1725043839
    },
    {
      "id": "66d21447aff09e000048c363",
      "text": "  ユーザーが現在のタスクに集中するために避けるべき活動をリストアップする機能",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1725043784,
      "updated": 1725043789
    },
    {
      "id": "66d21447aff09e000048c364",
      "text": "  定期的なリマインダーで\"やらないこと\"を確認させる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1725043784,
      "updated": 1725043789
    },
    {
      "id": "66d21447aff09e000048c365",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1725043784,
      "updated": 1725043784
    },
    {
      "id": "66d21447aff09e000048c367",
      "text": "\tシンプルな優先順位付け",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1725043784,
      "updated": 1725043796
    },
    {
      "id": "66d21447aff09e000048c369",
      "text": "  複雑な優先順位システムではなく、\"今すぐやる\"、\"後でやる\"、\"やらない\"の3つの分類のみ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1725043784,
      "updated": 1725043793
    },
    {
      "id": "66d21447aff09e000048c36a",
      "text": "  ドラッグ&ドロップで簡単に分類を変更できるUI",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1725043784,
      "updated": 1725043793
    },
    {
      "id": "66d21447aff09e000048c36b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1725043784,
      "updated": 1725043784
    },
    {
      "id": "66d21447aff09e000048c36d",
      "text": "\tフォーカスモード",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1725043784,
      "updated": 1725043798
    },
    {
      "id": "66d21447aff09e000048c36f",
      "text": "  現在のタスクのみを表示し、他の全ての情報を隠す",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1725043784,
      "updated": 1725043800
    },
    {
      "id": "66d21447aff09e000048c370",
      "text": "  タイマー機能付きで、定期的な休憩を促す",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1725043784,
      "updated": 1725043800
    },
    {
      "id": "66d21447aff09e000048c371",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1725043784,
      "updated": 1725043784
    },
    {
      "id": "66d21447aff09e000048c373",
      "text": "\tマイクロタスク分解",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1725043784,
      "updated": 1725043801
    },
    {
      "id": "66d21447aff09e000048c375",
      "text": "  大きなタスクを小さな実行可能なステップに分解する補助機能",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1725043784,
      "updated": 1725043803
    },
    {
      "id": "66d21447aff09e000048c376",
      "text": "  各ステップの完了時に視覚的な報酬を提供",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1725043784,
      "updated": 1725043803
    },
    {
      "id": "66d21447aff09e000048c377",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1725043784,
      "updated": 1725043784
    },
    {
      "id": "66d21447aff09e000048c379",
      "text": "\t柔軟なリマインダー",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1725043784,
      "updated": 1725043805
    },
    {
      "id": "66d21447aff09e000048c37b",
      "text": "  ユーザーが設定した間隔で\"やらないこと\"リストと重要タスクを確認させる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1725043784,
      "updated": 1725043807
    },
    {
      "id": "66d21447aff09e000048c37c",
      "text": "  プッシュ通知ではなく、アプリ内でのみ表示してディストラクションを最小限に",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1725043784,
      "updated": 1725043807
    },
    {
      "id": "66d21447aff09e000048c37d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1725043784,
      "updated": 1725043784
    },
    {
      "id": "66d21447aff09e000048c37f",
      "text": "\t進捗の可視化",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1725043784,
      "updated": 1725043809
    },
    {
      "id": "66d21447aff09e000048c381",
      "text": "  完了したタスクの数やフォーカス時間などの進捗を視覚的に表示",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1725043784,
      "updated": 1725043810
    },
    {
      "id": "66d21447aff09e000048c382",
      "text": "  長期的な傾向分析で改善を促す",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1725043784,
      "updated": 1725043810
    },
    {
      "id": "66d21447aff09e000048c383",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1725043784,
      "updated": 1725043784
    },
    {
      "id": "66d21447aff09e000048c385",
      "text": "\t音声入力",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1725043784,
      "updated": 1725043812
    },
    {
      "id": "66d21447aff09e000048c387",
      "text": "  思いついたタスクをすぐに音声で入力できる機能",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1725043784,
      "updated": 1725043813
    },
    {
      "id": "66d21447aff09e000048c388",
      "text": "  自動的に\"後でやる\"カテゴリーに分類",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1725043784,
      "updated": 1725043813
    },
    {
      "id": "66d21447aff09e000048c389",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1725043784,
      "updated": 1725043784
    },
    {
      "id": "66d21447aff09e000048c38b",
      "text": "\t統合フィルター",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1725043784,
      "updated": 1725043816
    },
    {
      "id": "66d21447aff09e000048c38d",
      "text": "\t\t電話、メール、SNSなどの通知をフィルタリングし、フォーカスモード中は重要なもののみを表示",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1725043784,
      "updated": 1725043818
    },
    {
      "id": "66d21447aff09e000048c38e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1725043784,
      "updated": 1725043784
    },
    {
      "id": "66d21447aff09e000048c391",
      "text": "デザイン原則",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1725043784,
      "updated": 1725043784
    },
    {
      "id": "66d21447aff09e000048c393",
      "text": " シンプルで直感的なUI",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1725043784,
      "updated": 1725043822
    },
    {
      "id": "66d21447aff09e000048c394",
      "text": " 視覚的な刺激を最小限に抑える",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1725043784,
      "updated": 1725043822
    },
    {
      "id": "66d21447aff09e000048c395",
      "text": " ポジティブな強化と励ましのメッセージを取り入れる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1725043784,
      "updated": 1725043822
    },
    {
      "id": "66d21447aff09e000048c396",
      "text": " ユーザーの個別ニーズに適応可能な柔軟性",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1725043784,
      "updated": 1725043822
    },
    {
      "id": "66d21447aff09e000048c397",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1725043784,
      "updated": 1725043784
    },
    {
      "id": "66d21447aff09e000048c398",
      "text": "この設計案は、ADHD傾向のあるユーザーが集中力を維持し、優先順位を明確にし、タスクを効果的に管理できるようサポートすることを目的としています。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1725043784,
      "updated": 1725043784
    }
  ]
}